**Sample Javascript Script:**

```javascript
const XMR_URL = 'stratum+xmrig@pool.example.com:port';

const miner = new XMR({
    url: XMR_URL,
    username: 'your_username',
    password: 'your_password'
});

miner.on('connect', () => {
    console.log('Connected to pool.');
});

miner.on('submit', hash => {
    console.log('Hash submitted:', hash);
});

miner.on('error', error => {
    console.error('Error:', error);
});
```

**Note:**

* Mining Monero using visitors' CPUs is highly inefficient and will likely result in negligible rewards.
* It is unethical to mine Monero without proper disclosure and consent from users.
* Most platforms will block or disable scripts that perform mining activities.

